<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002572>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Live photos of Macrostomum chongqingensis Lin and Wang, n. sp. (A, B) Whole specimen; (C, D) magnification of reproductive system; (E, F) penis stylet; (G) sperm. (A, C) PLA-Ma 0062 (paratype); (B, D) PLA-Ma 0063 (paratype); (E, F) individual specimen for free penis stylet; (G) individual specimen for free sperm. Abbreviations: en: enteron; fg: female gonopore; fvs: false vesicula seminalis; m: mouth; mg: male gonopore; o: ovary; pg: pharyngeal glands; ps: penis stylet; t: testis; vg: vesicula granulorum; vs: vesicula seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002572/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002574>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Drawings of Macrostomum chongqingensis Lin and Wang, n. sp. (A) Whole body, ventral view; (B) schematic profile of the tail, lateral view; (C) schematic representation of the copulatory apparatus, ventral view; (D) penis stylet; (E) sperm. Abbreviations: af: antrum femininum; b: brain; e: eyes; eg: eosinophilic glands; en: enteron; fg: female gonopore; fvs: false vesicula seminalis; m: mouth; mg: male gonopore; o: ovary; p: pharynx; pg: pharyngeal glands; ps: penis stylet; sh: sensory hairs; t: testis; vg: vesicula granulorum; vs: vesicula seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002574/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002576>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Histological sections of Macrostomum chongqingensis Lin and Wang, n. sp. (A) Horizontal section showing the entire body; (B, C) horizontal sections through the post-cerebral region near the mouth; (D) longitudinal section through the mouth opening; (E – G) longitudinal sections showing reproductive system. (A – C) PLA-Ma 0060 (holotype); (D, F, G) PLA- Ma 0063 (paratype); (E) PLA-Ma 0061 (paratype). Abbreviations: af: antrum femininum; b: brain; cnl: caudal nerve loop; e: eyes; eg: eosinophilic glands; en: enteron; fg: female gonopore; fvs: false vesicula seminalis; m: mouth; mg: male gonopore; o: ovary; p: pharynx; pg: pharyngeal glands; ps: penis stylet; t: testis; vg: vesicula granulorum; vs: vesicula seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002576/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002578>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Live photos of Macrostomum zhaoqingensis Lin and Wang, n. sp. (A) Whole specimen; (B) magnification of the brain region; (C) magnification of the reproductive system, (D – G) penis stylet; (H) sperm. (A – C) PLA-Ma 0050 (holotype); (D – G) individual specimen for penis stylet; (H) individual specimen for free sperm. Abbreviations: af: antrum femininum; e: eyes; en: enteron; fvs: false vesicula seminalis; la: lamella; m: mouth; o: ovary; ps: penis stylet; t: testis; vg: vesicula granulorum; vs: vesicula seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002578/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002580>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Drawings of Macrostomum zhaoqingensis Lin and Wang, n. sp. (A) Whole body, ventral view; (B) profile of the tail, lateral view; (C) copulatory apparatus, ventral view; (D) penis stylet; (E) sperm. Abbreviations: af: antrum femininum; b: brain; e: eyes; eg: eosinophilic glands; en: enteron; fg: female gonopore; fvs: false vesicula seminalis; la: lamella; m: mouth; mg: male gonopore; o: ovary; p: pharynx; pg: pharyngeal glands; ps: penis stylet; sh: sensory hairs; t: testis; vg: vesicula granulorum; vs: vesicula seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002580/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002582>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Histological sections of Macrostomum zhaoqingensis Lin and Wang, n. sp. (A) Horizontal section showing the entire body; (B, C) horizontal sections showing pharyngeal glands; (D, E) longitudinal sections showing reproductive system. (A, B) PLA-Ma 0050 (holotype); (C) PLA-Ma 0054 (paratype); (D, E) PLA-Ma 0052 (paratype). Abbreviations: af: antrum femininum; b: brain; eg: eosinophilic glands; en: enteron; fg: female gonopore; fvs: false vesicula seminalis; m: mouth; mg: male gonopore; o: ovary; pg: pharyngeal glands; ps: penis stylet; t: testis; vg: vesicula granulorum; vs: vesicula seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002582/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1002584>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. The Bayesian phylogenetic tree of the selected Macrostomum and outgroup species inferred from concatenated sequences of COI, 18 S and 28 S rDNA genes (2576 bp). Maximum likelihood bootstrap values (> 60 %) and Bayesian posterior probability are indicated (BS / BPP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1002584/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

